Today I want to talk about high school relationships. I got to tell you that they really don't work and if you think that it will then you're not thinking right. See for me, I made the mistake of thinking my relationship is bigger then what it is and I choose not to accept that no more. These conversations between us sticks into my head and really makes me think. I really don't know how to react but I guess I'll roll with the punches.
